            "text": "2. In his own name. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "Hide my commandments with thee",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "; lay them up in thy mind and heart with care, as men do their choicest treasures. ",
